steps.description:
* Use the Little Path on the Left
* Jump down and go into the Cave, Turn in / Accept Quests 
* Accept other quest in the west
* Leave Camp, Go NorthWest

* Accept Quest On Post Stand on the Street
* Kill Spiders
* Loot Eggs (BLUE)
* Kill Spider Boss (RED DOT)
* Go back on the Street up North
steps.tips: * Eggs don't need to to be Complete there are other spots later.

steps.description:
* Go to Ziz (Quest) Turn in  / Accept
* Kill Venture Corp Logger (VL)
* Kill Operator Until the Blueprints drop
* Go back to Ziz ( Turn in  / Accept Quest)
* Go West to Sun Rock Retreat
steps.tips: * You can after Ziz, go Up the Mountains (shortcut)

steps.description:
* Accept Quests Cycle of Rebirth / Boulderslide Ravine / Trouble in the Depps
* Get Flight spot
* Leave Camp, South East way (Back)
steps.tips: * Skip Quests for now (Elemental War / Harpies Threaten / Cenarius' Legacy)

steps.description:
* Go into the cave
* Loot Crystals
* Go straight through the Cave until you see on your left a little Plateau
* Get up the Plateau (Don't fall down in the Hole!)
* Leave Cave if the quest is Complete

* Turn in Quest
* Leave Stonetalon
* At the Barrens Border (Turn in Quest / Accept New)
* Go up North to Ashenvale

* Turn In Quest DON'T Accept Nugget Slugs 
* Go up North
* At the Ashenvale border Climb up the Tower Turn in Quest and Accept new
* Go to Ashenvale

* Move North
* Get the Report from the Scout
* Turn in Ashenvale Hunt (2 times) Accept New One
* Move the Street North East on the Street find the Outrider (Get Report)
* move Back the street south East 
* run trough the entire ashenvale zone west way!
steps.tips:
* if u have Inventory Problems (skip Reports, cancel quest)
*   it requires you to hold 3 quest Items

steps.description:
* Move all the way straight to West
* At the Alliance village (move southway around)
* get Flight point
* Turn in Quest By the Single Male Troll (in the west Hut)
* Accept Quest from the FEMALE troll (south Hut)
* Accept Elite Quest from the Orc in front of the Tent
* follow the ORC
* Turn In Quests / Fly back to Splintertree Post
* Move south to Barrens Borders Turn in Reports Quests
* HS to CrossRoads
steps.tips:
* if u play Solo, SKIP ELITE QUEST
* Grind on your way

steps.description:
* Move West (all the way)
* grind on the way
steps.tips: * Don't run trough the Alliance camp, go around south.

steps.description:
* if u don't have the Egg Hunt quest, Accept in CrossRoads
* Fly down to Camp Taurajo
steps.tips: * Always remind on Resupply! Repair!

steps.description:
* Accept ALL quest(s) in Camp Taurajo
* Go East and Look for "Owatanka" Blue thunderlizard / Kill / Loot Item
* GRIND this area if he is not there
* Accept Quest Item
* go Camp Taurajo To Turn in Quest
* Go South To make Egg Hunt
steps.tips: * you can refresh your Shard buff every tim you're in Taurajo, if need to

steps.description:
* Kill / Grind Silithid Mobs 
* loot Eggs from the Mound's 
* Look for a Elite (Harvester, lvl24) Spawn timer 2H45M
* Kill StormHide / Kodos / Gr thunderhawk (for Chens Keg)
* Go south

* Kill Warfrency / Seer / Skalter and loot (Shield  / Wand / Dagger)
* Kill the 3 Named (RED)
* Find NPC (Tauren) Walk on the Street Accept Quest
Go South East to the dwarfs

* Kill Excavator / Foreman
* Kill and Loot Khazgrom (Little Red Circle)
* Go back to GANN on the Street Turn in Accept Next Part
* MAKE SURE CHENs Quest is rdy / if not farm dat shit!
* HS back to Taurajo

* Turn in Quests Accept new one
* fly to CrossRoads

* Turn in Quests in XR
* Move East
* Kill Highlvl Zhevras loot Carcass
* Place Carcass on the DEAD TREE (BLUE)
* Go to Ratchet 
* Turn in ALL Quests
* Accept only "Further Instructions" (Stonetalon)
* Fly to Sun Rock Retreat in Stonetalon
steps.tips:
* After turning in Egg Hunt; Destroy every remaining Egg
* After turning in Deepmoss Spider Eggs; Destroy every remaining Egg
* Chens is now a repeatable quest (No EXP, SKIP)

steps.description:
* Look For the Kolkar Messanger (BLUE)
* Kill him and loot Letter (if u don't find him, leave it)
* Move to the Freewind Post

* Turn in All Quest
* Accept ALL new
* get Flight Point
* GO Down the Lift and go north
steps.tips: * Don't forget the quest on the POSTER

steps.description:
* Kill All Galaks
* Go east until u see a Ramp in the wall
* Go up, Accept Quest
* just jump (or walk) off the wooden plank, to complete the quest
* Skip next Quest (Elite)
* Go east

* Kill Gravelsnout until the Ore Drops (20% drop chance, very few mobs)
* Loot the Alien Egg (BLUE) on your Gravelsnout Killroute
* make sure you're at least 2 bars away from level 26 (90%)
* go back to the Lift and go up to Freewind Post
steps.tips: * use "/tar gra" to find the Gravelsnout

steps.description:
* Turn in Quests / Accept new 
* Kill Thunderhawk's (Flying Snakes) (drop chance 100%)
* Go back to Taurajo
* Turn in Quest; SKIP "Mahren Skyseer"
* Fly to Ashenvale - Splintertree Post
steps.tips: * If you don't have it try to Kill "Harvester" and "Washte Pawne" in the South.

steps.description:
* Accept Quest From Pixie
* Accept Quest from the Orc Mastok
* Make This your new HOME
* Go south to the new 
* Kill Outrunner (NightElfs)
* Kill Sharptalon is lvl 30 be careful ( S ), Loot item
* Move West to Orc. accept quest
steps.tips:
* Skip Warsong Supplies - not worth!
* if you have the "Update Outrunner Report" quest, abort.

steps.description:
* Help Torek and kill every Nightelf
* Move West Way to the Lake
* kill waterelementals 
* look for Tideress " /tar tid ", kill and loot quest Item / Accept it.
* move into the Little Light on the island in the middle of the lake
* Go West
steps.tips:
* If you play in a group, Kill Tideress AND next step Ursangous first 
** (need the respawn Respawn!)

steps.description:
* Kill the Named Bear "Ursangous" Loot item / accept it
* Grind our way NorthEast

* Kill Black Cat Shadumbra, Loot item, Accept
* Kill Sisters and loot until u find Etched Phial
* Go south

* go into the Moonwell (Fountain) use, Phial (Inventory)
* Port back to Splintertree Post

* Turn in Quests, Accept ONLY Je'neu of the Earthen Ring
* Fly to Zoram'gar Outpost (Ashenvale WEST)

* Turn in Quest (Don't accept Dungeon quests)
* Accept Troll Charm, Between a Rock and a Thistlefur
* Move East ways

* Kill All NPC you see, fight your way up into A Cave
* Loot Troll Charms from little Troll Chests on the Ground (in the North cave)
* Accept the Escort Quest (hard, 3-4 mobs at the same time)
* if everything finish, go back to the camp on the West
* Turn in Every Quest Accept Elite (if in a gap) 
* Hearthstone back to Splintertree Post.
steps.tips:
* before escort quest finish Troll Charm!
* in a group Accept Elite Quest

steps.description:
* Turn in Quest in the Inn, leave the Camp
* Go on the Street, turn in Quest
* Go South East, On a Little Hill between 2 Totem, Place Flag
* Fight mob waves back, Kill Elite 
* GO north, go uo the TreeHouse until the very top 
* kill the 3 NPC, Loot Head
* GO East Ways

* GO North
* Kill Satyr
* WALK back to Splintertree Post, turn in Quest, 
* Fly West, to Zoram'gar Outpost
* Turn in Quests
* fly to Run Rock Retreat (Stonetalon)

* Turn in Bloodelf quest / SKIP "THE DEN"
* go to the Tauren next to the in Accept "Bloodfury Bloodline"
* Make Sun Rock Retreat your Home
* Go Through the west Pass
* Kill Elite Harpy 
* GRIND! to 28
* HS back to Sun Rock Retreat
* Turn In Quest
* Fly to Thunderbluff
steps.tips: * Grind until you have 95% of lvl 27

steps.description:
* In Front of the Chieftain, Turn in Quest
* Get your lvl 28 Class Spells 
* Bind yourself in the TB inn (Hearthstone)
* Fly to Thousand Needles

* Turn in Quest in Freewind Post / Accept new
* Go down and Go north into the Kolkar Cave
* Keep Left in the Cave until u see a Violet Flame
* use it, Loot Hoof
* Move North

* Look out for the Messanger if u don't already have the assa quest.
* Move to the Whitereach Post
* Accept all Quest / turn in all Quests 
* Go back to the Boiling water, Loot Agaves from the Ground (Plant).

* Kill LvL 30 Cat in Cage ( C ), Loot item
* Look for SteelSnap (BLUE PATH) Kill, Loot Item
* if you Done, GO up the Ramp
* Loot Eggs on the Ground ( E )
* kill all mobs
* Do Escort Quest.
* Go Back Whitereach, Turn in Quest.
* HS to Thunderbluff
steps.tips: * Go Up, do the escort Quest, if  only 1-2 Eggs, r missing

steps.description:
* Turn in Quest in Hunter Rise, Accept New
* Turn in Quest in Elders Ruse, Accept New
* fly back to Thousand Needles.
* MAKE 1k NEEDLES YOUR NEW HOME
steps.tips: * Learn new Skills if don't

steps.description:
* Turn in Quests
* GO down the Elevator 
* Move West ways until you reached the Ramp
* Loot The Documents first (BLUE)
* Kill the Elite on the graveyard (set the Bon-Fire Lit), Loot Item
* Move north to kill Named, Loot item
* Accept Escort Quest. 
* Move West way
steps.tips: * MAKE 1k NEEDLES YOUR NEW HOME

steps.description:
* Turn in Quest 
* Make sure you are lvl 29 by now!
* HS back to Freewind Post
* Turn in all Quest
* FLY TO Orgrimmar!

* Make OG your New HOME
* Leave OG to Direction Zeppelin! 
* Get On the UNDERCITY Zeppelin (ZEP on the South side!)
steps.tips: * Learn new 30 Skills!

steps.description:
* Jump Down the Zeppelin,
* Move South, Swim as fast as u can!
* Fight your way to Tarrens Mill
* Turn in / Accept ALL Quest
steps.tips: * Skip Humbert's Sword

steps.description:
* Kill Turtle Loot 10 "Turtle Meat" for a LATER QUEST
* Kill Bears Loot Item (10)
* Kill Spiders Loot Item (1)

* fast Side Quest, Don't Waist time
* Loot Blood from NPC
* Kill 2 Named Mobs, Loot Keys
* free Orcs (Use Key on the Chains on there feet)
* Leave

* Kill Spiders (S) / Bears (B) / Cats (C) until Quest is Rdy
* Loot All Mushrooms on the Field
* Go Back To Tarrens Mill

* Turn in Quests Accept New
* Go to Inn (Big House)
* Accept Quests For Cooking, Buy outside the house (Right) 1x Soothing Spices
* Turn in Cooking Quest
* Go SW to the yeti cave

* Go into the Cave until Helcular's Rod Dropt (Extrem low drop chance)
* Go back to Tarrens Mill
* Turn in Quest Accept next Part
* Go back to the Cave 
* Use the Rod on top and Water area Flame (only 2 flames are in this cave!)
* Leave Cave move East

* use Potion on Dog
* Kill Every Named (RED DOTS)
* Kill farmers
* Go to the Mine South 
* Go first in the Lower entrance, if he's not there Check the entire Mine
* Grind until hit 31
* Die on purpose; Rezz at TM

* Turn in Quest 
* SKIP battle For Hillsbrand (kill 15 Peasants)
* Move East Way Arathi Highlands
